Smith Corona 1903A3 Springfield, chambered .30-06. This rifle was sporterized at some point in its life; as such, the receiver is drilled and tapped. - Stock- All stock hardware- Front sight- Rear sight- Bolt- Trigger guard / magazine assembly- Trigger
